# Story File Template

Created only when status changes to `In progress`.

```markdown
# {ID} — {Title}

## Description
[What the user needs and why]

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Criterion 1
- [ ] Criterion 2

## Technical Notes
[Implementation approach, affected files, dependencies]

## Status
- **Priority**: ASAP / High / Medium / Low
- **Status**: Pending / In progress / In review / Blocked / On hold / Completed / Cancelled
- **Created**: YYYY-MM-DD
- **Completed**: YYYY-MM-DD (fill when done)
- **Blocked reason**: (fill if Blocked/On hold/Cancelled)
```
